Really good.  I wish I knew what hardware and software you used to make 
it.  Great editing to bring shots together to imply new footage; lovely 
tempo, and sense of emotion and drama.  Matching images with music and 
sounds is spot on and the music overall really brings it together.  One 
small criticism: Some of the shots are too easily identifyable and this 
needn't be the case with more searching but I appreciate this is no small 
task.  Shots like these  need to be cut so short that only by 
freeze-framing it would it be possible to identify it.  Back to the 
positive, you're really honing your movie-making skills.  Maybe one day...﻿
